data.description: Amazing opportunity! Bring your toys, boats, RVs, tools! Large 2 bay detached shop and adorable spacious ranch with porches that overlook the beautiful setting on 1.3-/+ unrestricted acres. This home offers an on suite master, a flowing cozy open floor plan, and a fourth bedroom that could be converted to additional living, office, or play space. The porches are perfect for lounging in the evenings. New windows, updated finishes, no detail spared to make this a move in ready home. Level yard with fenced area for play. Large above ground pool can stay or go. Located with an easy drive to Gainesville, Demorest, Clarkesville, or Helen. Priced to sell.
